      <title>英国制裁中国公司在对俄罗斯的供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/uk-sanctions-chinese-firms-in-clampdown-on-supplies-to-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国对这10家基于中国的公司实施了制裁，该公司称俄罗斯的国防工业是其自2022年以来针对弗拉基米尔·普京政权的最大经济措施的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/uk-sanctions-chinese-firms-in-clampdown-on-supplies-to-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 18:25:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将马斯克命令向联邦工人命令“天才”举动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/trump-hails-musk-order-to-federal-workers-as-genius-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统为亿万富翁顾问埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的努力辩护，迫使联邦工人证明其角色和生产力是合理的，或被解雇，这是为了使美国政府中的欺诈和浪费扎根的合法性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/trump-hails-musk-order-to-federal-workers-as-genius-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 18:07:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克总理敦促更多的国防支出，改革欧盟的财政规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/czech-premier-urges-more-defense-spending-revamp-of-eu-s-fiscal-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克总理彼得拉·菲亚拉（Petr Fiala）表示，他的国家将需要在未来几年内将国防支出提高到至少3％的经济产出，呼吁欧盟大修其财政规则以允许这种投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/czech-premier-urges-more-defense-spending-revamp-of-eu-s-fiscal-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 17:44:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>萨默斯（Summers</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/summers-calls-us-demands-in-ukraine-talks-beyond-versailles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前财政部长劳伦斯·萨默斯（Lawrence Summers）谴责特朗普政府在乌克兰将其一部分自然资源移交给美国的压力，在过去的重大冲突中对美国传统有了彻底的区别。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/summers-calls-us-demands-in-ukraine-talks-beyond-versailles</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 17:35:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普威胁接管时，华盛顿特区市长呼吁建国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/washington-dc-mayor-re-ups-call-for-statehood-as-trump-threatens-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市长穆里尔·鲍瑟（Muriel Bowser）从大规模联邦裁员中捍卫地方治理，因为她从大规模联邦裁员开始向华盛顿特区进行经济袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/washington-dc-mayor-re-ups-call-for-statehood-as-trump-threatens-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 17:32:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅尔斯与盟友进行谈判，急于通过德国国防资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/merz-in-talks-with-german-allies-to-rush-through-defense-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，德国总理在等待的弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）与社会民主党人进行了会谈，以迅速提高国防支出，然后才能完成一项正式的联盟协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/merz-in-talks-with-german-allies-to-rush-through-defense-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 17:23:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟在特朗普迫在眉睫的金属贸易争端中扩大关税清单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/eu-expands-tariff-list-in-trump-s-looming-metals-trade-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士说，如果美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）遵循他对钢铁和铝制出口施加职责的威胁，欧洲联盟正在扩大将以报复性关税为目标的美国商品清单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/eu-expands-tariff-list-in-trump-s-looming-metals-trade-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 17:07:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bessent，国会中的共和党人踢开始减税谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/bessent-republicans-in-congress-to-hold-weekly-tax-cut-meetings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）和国会领导人将开始每周开会，因为共和党人希望塑造削减税款，并以年底的截止日期为止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/bessent-republicans-in-congress-to-hold-weekly-tax-cut-meetings</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 16:55:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的“您做了什么”电子邮件从联邦工会那里绘制诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/musk-what-did-you-do-email-draws-suit-from-federal-unions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代表数千名联邦雇员的工会向特朗普政府起诉埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的周末电子邮件，要求他们解释上周的成就或被解雇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/musk-what-did-you-do-email-draws-suit-from-federal-unions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 15:53:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与盟友归咎于乌克兰的俄罗斯战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/g-7-may-forgo-joint-statement-in-rupture-over-ukraine-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统加深了华盛顿与盟友在乌克兰的分裂，撤回了美国对俄罗斯2022年在联合国和七国集团中的入侵的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/g-7-may-forgo-joint-statement-in-rupture-over-ukraine-stance</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 13:03:14 GMT</pubDate>
